data.description: Welcome to your future home in the charming Silver Springs Shores community!Be sure to ask how you may be able to qualify to purchase this home with no down payment. This spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem is now available for you to make your own. With a host of desirable features and a fantastic location, this property offers a delightful blend of comfort, style, and convenience. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the tastefully laid ceramic tile flooring in the kitchen, creating an elegant and low-maintenance space that's perfect for meal preparation and casual dining. The kitchen is sure to be the heart of your home, ideal for family gatherings and culinary adventures. A standout feature of this home is the generously proportioned Master Bedroom. It provides ample space for your personal retreat, with ceramic tile accents in the master bath that add an element of sophistication and ease of maintenance. The guest bathroom also boasts ceramic tile, ensuring a cohesive and attractive aesthetic throughout. The cozy carpeted bedrooms offer a warm and inviting atmosphere, providing the ideal spaces for relaxation and rest. The living room showcases vinyl flooring, combining practicality with style. Whether you're entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet evening in, this versatile space will meet all your needs. Step outside, and you'll be greeted by a fantastic above-ground pool with an accompanying deck. Summertime fun and relaxation are just steps away. The privacy-fenced backyard ensures you can unwind and soak up the sun in complete seclusion, creating your own personal oasis. And for those cool evenings, you'll find a built-in fire pit in the pool deck, perfect for cozy gatherings and marshmallow roasting. Location is everything, and this home is conveniently situated near Silver Springs State Park, offering endless opportunities for outdoor adventures, picnics, and exploration. Shopping and schools are also close by, making it easy for you to access everything you need within minutes. Your dream home awaits, offering comfort, style, and a superb location that's hard to beat. Schedule a viewing today and start creating the memories of a lifetime in your new home. Roof is 2007.
